c: 6
v: 104
t: "Nabiyow ama korosuk Nummah sin Rabbik tirtoó kee cakki gitak makkootaanam edde tablen Baxxaqqooqii kee Sumaq siinih yemeeteh, cakki yableeh Nummaysa num toysa isi Nafsi kah yablem, cakki able waah cakkik makkķkoota num isi Nafsi finqisam, anu sin taamoomi dacrisa num hinniyo anu cagalah Yallih farmo gudduysa numuk kal keenik ixxic"